en: Strike the ball with a <color=green>dash</color> to make it <color=red>deadly</color>
br: Strike the ball with a <color=green>dash</color> to make it <color=red>deadly</color>

en: <color=red>Push</color> other players off the raft!                                                                  Beware, the fences break!
br: <color=red>Empurre</color> outros jogadores para fora da jangada!                                                                  Cuidado, as cercas quebram!

en: Pass the <color=#BEAE2E>belt</color> to others before the<color=red> Luchador strikes</color>!
br: Passe o <color=#BEAE2E>cinturão</color> para outros jogadores antes do<color=red> Luchador atacar</color>!

en: Game Paused                                Press P to resume
br: Jogo Pausado                                      Pressione P para voltar

en: Stay on the Oasis to fill your <color=red>bar</color>. The first player to fill the <color=red>bar</color> wins.
br: Fique dentro dos Oasis para preencher a sua <color=red>barra</color>. O primeiro jogador que preencher a <color=red>barra</color> vence!

en: Collect the <color=red>Donut Bullet</color> and use your <color=green>dash</color> to shoot it at your opponents.
br: Colete a <color=red>Rosquinha</color> e em seguida use o <color=green>Dash</color> para atirar ela nos seus adversários.

en: Score <color=red>goals</color> at your opponents to eliminate them!
br: Faça <color=red>gol</color> nos seus adversários para eliminar eles

en: Defend the <color=red>goals</color> with your color to stay alive!
br: Defenda a <color=red>goleira</color> da sua cor para se manter vivo

en: Collect the <color=red>flowers</color> and deliver them to the cows. The first player that delivers 10 flowers to the cows wins!
br: Colete as <color=red>flores</color> e leve até as vacas. O primeiro jogador que entregar 10 flores para as vacas ganha!

en: Collect the <color=green>yakisobas</color> to increase the size of your <color=red>dragon</color>. Use the <color=red>dragon's</color> body to eliminate the other players.
br: Colete os <color=green>yakisobas</color> para aumentar seu <color=red>dragão</color>. Use o corpo do <color=red>dragão</color> para eliminar os outros jogadores.

en: Are you sure you want to quit the game?
br: Tem certeza de que deseja sair do jogo?
